    "instruction": "Load metric.csv and trace.csv from the current working directory. For each file report the overall timestamp range (min and max timestamp). Then for metric.csv: group by cmdb_id and kpi_name and compute count, P95, P90, P50 (median), and P5 of the value column for each group; return the grouped table limited to top 50 rows sorted by count descending. For trace.csv: group by cmdb_id and trace_name and compute count, P95, P90, P50, and P5 of the value column for each group; return the grouped table limited to top 50 rows sorted by count descending. Keep outputs compact (only the requested aggregates and timestamp ranges)."
